v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Khuy%E1%BA%BFn-h%E1%BB%8Dc/poem-HPqEmUiX0JHD3yZpQ6V6ZQ">Khuyến học - 勸學</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/L%C3%A2m-chung-di-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-I86uGQtK3uDAayDqWSRvWw">Lâm chung di chiếu - 臨終遺詔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-sMXrZTDvW5uflSvv6NTMXQ">Lý Nhân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ph%C3%BA/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Quang-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-c%E1%BA%A3m-th%C3%A0nh/poem-USSHIXv-7jRQ7Jt3qyrdiA">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Quang Đức điện thượng cảm thành” - 奉和御製光德殿上感成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ph%C3%BA/author-6psImpn4SbleLfrcnYcyQA">Phạm Đạo Phú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Thi%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8B-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-7_zF-x1x1pienpNIOQCVKQ">Thiện vị chiếu - 禪位詔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-VI/poem-e_GlxdsNOQdzuQuxh1cLCQ">Vô đề (VI) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br></div>	</div>
